        Spell/Skill Help: help <spell_name/skill_name>

        
         *Note: The spells listed 'like' this, indicated the
		key word to use for the help.  
                Example: help missile
        

        Usage for spells: cast '<spell_name>'
        Usage for skills: <skill_name>

	See also: spells, skills
